<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Welcome Letter</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #000;">

  <div
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #333; line-height: 1.5; width: 100%; margin: 0 auto; border: 1px solid #eee; position: relative;">



    <!-- HEADER BANNER -->

    <div style="width: 100%; height: auto;background-color: #eef1f8;margin-bottom:-60px;">

      <!-- <img src="banner2.jpg" alt="Zextra Travel Assist" style="width: 100%; display: block;"> -->

      <img src="<%= policy.wel_banner2Base64 %>" alt="Zextra Travel Assist" style="width: 100%; display: block;">

    </div>



    <div style="padding:0 10px 0px 10px;background-color: #eef1f8;">

      <!-- <div

                style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 10px; padding: 25px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); border: 1px solid #f0f0f0; min-height: 120px; position: relative; z-index: 1;"> -->

      <div
        style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px 10px;padding-bottom: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); border: 1px solid #f0f0f0; min-height: 120px; position: relative; z-index: 1;">



        <!-- WELCOME LABEL & DATE -->

        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: -44px; position: relative; z-index: 10;">

          <tr>

            <!-- <td align="center" style="padding-left: 20px;"> -->

            <td align="center">

              <div
                style="background-color: rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.7); color: white; padding: 10px 30px; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">

                <h3 style="padding: 0;margin: 0;line-height: 1;">WELCOME LETTER</h3>

              </div>

            </td>

          </tr>

          <tr style="position: relative;top:-35px;">

            <td align="right" style="padding-right:20px; vertical-align:bottom;">



              <span style="

                                background-color:#e1e9f3;

                                padding:4px 12px;

                                border-radius:6px;

                                font-weight:bold;

                                color:#000000;

                                display:inline-block;

                                font-size:16px;

                            ">

                Date: <%= customerDate %>

              </span>



            </td>

          </tr>

        </table>



        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">

          <tr>

            <td style="vertical-align: top;">

              <p style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0; color: #333;line-height: 1;"><strong>Dear,</strong>

              </p>

              <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #000; margin: 0;">
                 <%= customerName %>,
              </p>





              <div
                style="width: 100%;height: 2px;background: #2d7ff9;position: relative;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px;">

                <!-- <span style="width: 10px;height: 10px;background: #2d7ff9;border-radius: 50%;position: absolute;right: 0;top: -4px;"></span> -->

              </div>



              <h2
                style="margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 0; color: #333; font-weight: 600;font-size: 15px;line-height: 1;">

                Welcome and Thank You for Choosing</h2>

              <h1 style="margin: 0;margin-top: 5px; color: #0056b3; font-size: 16px;line-height: 1;">
                ZextrA Travel Assist

              </h1>

              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 10px;">by Interstellar Services Private Limited ("Company")

              </p>



            </td>

          </tr>

        </table>

      </div>



      <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"
        style="margin-top:-140px; position:relative; z-index:10;">

        <tr>

          <td align="right">



            <table width="280" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="

                    background-image:url('<%= policy.wel_creditBase64 %>'); 

                    background-repeat:no-repeat;

                    background-size:cover;

                    width:360px;

                    height:180px;

                    color:#ffffff;

                    font-family:Arial, sans-serif;

                    border-radius:12px;

                    margin-top:10px;

                ">

              <tr>

                <td colspan="2" style="padding:15px 20px 0 10px;">

                  <div style="padding: 0px 0px 5px 0px; font-size:15px; ">

                    ZextrA Travel Assist Card

                  </div>

                  <div style="font-size:10px;">Travel Assistance No.</div>

                  <div style="font-size:20px; line-height: 1;">
                    <%= assistanceNumber %>

                  </div>

                </td>

               <!-- QR Code -->
                <td style="padding: 9px 9px 0px 5px; width:20%;" align="right">
                  <img src="<%= policy.downloadUrlQrCodeBase64 %>" 
                       style="display: block; width: 80px !important; height: 80px !important; max-width: 80px !important; min-width: 80px !important; border-radius: 4px;">
                </td>

              </tr>



              <tr>

                <td style="padding:5px 10px 0px 10px; font-size:10px;">

                  Date of Departure<br>(from India)<br>

                  <strong>
                    <%= departureDate %>
                  </strong>

                </td>



                <td style="padding:5px 10px 0px 10px; font-size:10px;">

                  Date of Arrival<br>(in India)<br>

                  <strong>
                   <%= arrivalDate %>
                  </strong>

                </td>



                <td style="padding:5px 20px 0px 10px; font-size:10px;">

                  Duration of Travel<br>

                  <strong>
                     <%= travelDuration %>

                  </strong>

                </td>



              </tr>



              <tr>

                <td colspan="3" style="padding:4px 10px 10px 10px;">

                  <div style="font-size:11px;">

                    Insurance Policy/Certificate Number

                  </div>



                  <div style="font-size:20px;font-weight: 700;">

                    <%= policyNumber %>

                  </div>

                </td>

              </tr>



            </table>



          </td>

        </tr>

      </table>



      <!-- Second White Box -->

      <div style="

                        background-color:#ffffff;

                        border-radius:10px;

                        padding:30px 0px 0px 0px;

                        margin-top:-30px;

                        box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);

                        border:1px solid #f0f0f0;

                    ">



        <!-- INFO BOXES -->

        <div style="padding:0 10px;">

          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
            style="margin-bottom:20px;margin-top:20px; text-align:center;">



            <tr>

              <!-- Traveller -->

              <td width="25%" valign="top" style="border:2px solid #2b6cb0; border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden;">



                <div style="

                    background: linear-gradient(to right, #1f5fae, #3b8de3);

                    color:#ffffff;

                    padding:8px;

                    font-size:11px;

                    font-weight:bold;

                    text-align:left;

                    padding-left:10px;

                    height: 26px;

                    border-radius: 8px;

                ">

                  Traveller

                </div>



                <div style="

                    padding:10px 10px;

                    font-size:12px;

                    color:#333;

                    min-height:45px;

                    font-weight: 600;

                ">

                  <%= customerName %>

                </div>

              </td>



              <td width="3%"></td>



              <!-- Address -->

              <td width="44%" valign="top" style="border:2px solid #2b6cb0; border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden;">



                <div style="

                    background: linear-gradient(to right, #1f5fae, #3b8de3);

                    color:#ffffff;

                    padding:8px;

                    font-size:11px;

                    font-weight:bold;

                    text-align:left;

                    padding-left:10px;

                    height: 26px;

                    border-radius:8px;

                    font-weight: 600;

                ">

                  Address

                </div>



                <div style="

                    padding:10px;

                    font-size:12px;

                    color:#333;

                    min-height:40px;

                    line-height:1.3;

                    border-radius:8px;

                    font-weight: 600;">

                  <%= customerAddress %>
                </div>

              </td>



              <td width="3%"></td>



              <!-- Charges -->

              <td width="25%" valign="top" style="border:2px solid #2b6cb0; border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden;">



                <div style="

                    background: linear-gradient(to right, #1f5fae, #3b8de3);

                    color:#ffffff;

                    padding:8px;

                    font-size:11px;

                    font-weight:bold;

                    text-align:left;

                    padding-left:10px;

                    height: 26px;

                    border-radius:8px;

                    font-weight: 600;

                ">

                  Travel Assistance Charges<br>

                  (Incl. of GST)

                </div>



                <div style="

                    padding:10px 10px;

                    font-size:15px;

                    font-weight:500;

                    color:#333;

                    min-height:45px;

                    border-radius:8px;

                ">

                  ₹ <%= assistanceCharges %>

                </div>

              </td>

            </tr>



          </table>

        </div>



        <!-- MAIN BODY TEXT -->

        <div style="padding:0 10px;">

          <p style="color: #444; font-size: 12px;margin:6px 0;line-height: 1.3;">We are pleased to welcome you

            and introduce you to a unique

            offering curated by the Company — a <span style="color: #0056b3; font-weight: bold;">bundled

              overseas

              travel support package that includes access to global travel assistance services along with

              a

              travel

              insurance policy</span>, underwritten by a leading insurance company in India.</p>

        </div>



        <div style="padding:0 10px;">

          <p style="font-size: 12px;margin:6px 0;line-height: 1.3;">This value-added offering has been

            thoughtfully designed to enhance your

            travel experience and provide peace of mind during your journey. While the Company has

            facilitated and marketed this bundled product for your convenience, please note that the travel

            insurance and travel assistance services are independently provided by third-party service

            providers with whom you are directly connected through this arrangement. </p>

        </div>

        <div style="padding:0 10px;">

          <p style="font-size: 12px;margin:6px 0;line-height: 1.3;">The Company does not underwrite, issue, or

            service the insurance policy,

            nor does it provide travel assistance services. Our role is limited to facilitating access to

            this bundled solution and assisting you in connecting with the respective service providers.</p>

        </div>

        <div style="padding:0 10px;">

          <p style="font-size: 12px;margin:5px 0;line-height: 1.3;">We strongly encourage you to carefully

            read and understand the insurance

            policy wordings and the service terms provided by the respective service providers to fully

            understand the scope of coverage and assistance available to you.</p>

        </div>



        <h3
          style="text-decoration: underline; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 5px;padding:0 10px;margin-top:5px;line-height: 1.3;">

          What you

          can expect from

          this

          bundled offering:</h3>

        <div style="padding:0 10px;">

          <ul
            style="margin-top: 0; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 12px;font-weight: 600;margin-bottom:10px;line-height: 1.3;">

            <li>24x7 overseas travel assistance from a reputed service provider.</li>

            <li>Travel insurance cover (please read the policy wordings before you travel. Brief details as

              below).</li>

            <li>Ongoing support from the Company in helping you navigate and access these services</li>

          </ul>

        </div>



        <!-- BUTTON -->

        <div style="margin:0;">

          <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">

            <tr>

              <td
                style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #1f5fae, #2f73c8);color: white;padding: 3px 0 3px 20px;border-radius: 0 15px 15px 0;">

                To Know more about Travel Assistance

                <a href="<%= policy.assistLink %>" target="_blank"
                  style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #52a0ff, #2f73c8); color: white; padding: 5px 15px; border-radius: 15px; text-decoration: none; margin-left: 10px; font-weight: bold;    box-shadow: rgba(60, 64, 67, 0.3) 0px 1px 2px 0px, rgba(60, 64, 67, 0.15) 0px 2px 6px 2px;">Click

                  here</a>

              </td>

            </tr>

          </table>

        </div>



        <div style="padding:0 10px;">

          <p style="font-size: 12px;margin: 5px 0;">We appreciate your trust in the Company and will use our

            best efforts in

            supporting you in every way possible during your overseas journey.</p>

        </div>



        <p style="font-style: italic; color: #0056b3; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;padding:0 10px;margin:5px 0;">

          Wishing

          you safe,

          smooth,

          and memorable travels.</p>



        <!-- FOOTER WITH BACKGROUND IMAGE -->

        <div
          style="width: 100%; height: 150px;background: url('<%= policy.wel_footerbottomBase64 %>') no-repeat right bottom; background-size: contain; position: relative;">

          <div style="padding: 5px 20px; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0;">

            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;margin-top:5px">Warm regards,

            </p>

            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;margin-top:0px">

              <strong>For, ZextrA Travel Assist</strong>

            </p>

            <div style="text-align: left;">

              <img src="<%= policy.CompanyLogoImageBase64 %>" alt="Company Logo"
                style="max-width: 100px;max-height: 35px;margin-left: 40px;">

            </div>

            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;margin-top:0;">

              <span style="font-size: 10px;">by Interstellar Services Private Limited</span>

            </p>



            <div
              style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #1f5fae, #2f73c8); color: white; display: inline-block; padding: 3px 15px; font-size: 12px;margin-left: -20px;">

              Customer Services Support Team</div>

            <p style="margin: 5px 0; font-size: 11px; color: #333;">

              Email id: backoffice@interstellar.co.in | Contact No: +91 9967915569

            </p>

          </div>

        </div>



      </div>



      <!-- OVERLAPPING BLUE CARD SECTION -->



      <!-- DISCLAIMER -->

      <div style="padding: 5px 20px;  font-size: 9px; color: #777; text-align: justify; border-top: 1px solid #eee;">

        <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Interstellar Services Private Limited acts solely as a facilitator. The

        Company

        is not an insurance company or intermediary. All claims and service-related matters are to be addressed

        directly with the respective third-party service providers.

      </div>



    </div>



    <!-- DISCLAIMER -->

    <div style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #a6cefe, #e1eeff);

             height:2px;  font-size: 9px; color: #777; text-align: justify; border-top: 1px solid #eee;">



    </div>



  </div>



  <div style="text-align: center;">

    <img src="<%= logoImage %>" alt="Company Logo" style="max-width: 100px;max-height: 50px;">
  </div>

  <h5 style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin: 0 0 20px 0; padding: 0;">WELCOME LETTER
  </h5>



  <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start;">
    <div style="width: 60%;">
      <% const addressLines=customerAddress.length> 60
        ? customerAddress.match(/(.{1,60})(?:,|$)/g) // split by 70 chars at commas
        : [customerAddress];
        %>
        <p><strong>Dear</strong>
          <%= customerName %>,<br>
            <% addressLines.forEach(line=> { %>
              <%= line.trim() %><br>
                <% }) %>
                  <%= customerEmail %>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div style="width: 40%; text-align: right;">
      <p><strong>Date:</strong>
        <%= customerDate %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>



  <p>Welcome and Thank You for Choosing <strong>Interstellar Services Private Limited</strong> (“Company”)!</p>
  <p>We are pleased to welcome you and introduce you to a unique offering curated by the Company — a bundled overseas
    travel support package that includes access to global travel assistance services along with a travel insurance
    policy, underwritten by a leading insurance company in India.</p>
  <p>This value-added offering has been thoughtfully designed to enhance your travel experience and provide peace of
    mind during your journey. While the Company has facilitated and marketed this bundled product for your convenience,
    please note that the travel insurance and travel assistance services are independently provided by third-party
    service providers with whom you are directly connected through this arrangement.The Company does not underwrite,
    issue, or service the insurance policy, nor does it provide travel assistance services. Our role is limited to
    facilitating access to this bundled solution and assisting you in connecting with the respective service providers.
  </p>
  <p>The terms, conditions, coverage details, claims process, and servicing of the travel insurance policy are governed
    by the issuing insurance company. Similarly, the travel assistance services will be rendered by the respective
    travel assistance company as per their own terms of engagement.</p>
  <p>We strongly encourage you to carefully read and understand the insurance policy wordings and the service terms
    provided by the respective service providers to fully understand the scope of coverage and assistance available to
    you.</p>
  <p>What you can expect from this bundled offering:</p>
  <ul style="margin-top: 0;">
    <li>24x7 overseas travel assistance from a reputed service provider.</li>
    <li>Travel insurance cover (please read the policy wordings before you travel. Brief details as below).</li>
    <li>Ongoing support from the Company in helping you navigate and access these services.</li>
  </ul>

  <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 10px;">
    <tr>
      <th style="border: 1px solid #000; padding: 5px; text-align: left;">Date of Departure (from India)</th>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #000; padding: 5px; text-align: left;">
        <%= departureDate %>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th style="border: 1px solid #000; padding: 5px; text-align: left;">Date of Arrival (in India)</th>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #000; padding: 5px; text-align: left;">
        <%= arrivalDate %>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th style="border: 1px solid #000; padding: 5px; text-align: left;">Duration of Travel</th>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #000; padding: 5px; text-align: left;">
        <%= travelDuration %>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th style="border: 1px solid #000; padding: 5px; text-align: left;">Insurance Policy/Certificate Number</th>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #000; padding: 5px; text-align: left;">
        <%= policyNumber %>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th style="border: 1px solid #000; padding: 5px; text-align: left;">Travel Assistance Number</th>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #000; padding: 5px; text-align: left;">
        <%= assistanceNumber %>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th style="border: 1px solid #000; padding: 5px; text-align: left;">Travel Assistance Charges (Incl. of GST)</th>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #000; padding: 5px; text-align: left;">
        <%= assistanceCharges.includes('₹') ? assistanceCharges : `₹ ${assistanceCharges}` %>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>


  <p>To Know more about Travel Assistance, <a href="<%= policy.assistLink %>"
      style="color: #0066cc; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: bold;">Click here</a>.</p>
  <p>We appreciate your trust in the Company and will use our best efforts in supporting you in every way possible
    during your overseas journey.
    Wishing you safe, smooth, and memorable travels.</p>

  <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
    <p>Warm regards,<br>For, <strong>Interstellar Services Private Limited</strong></p>
    <br>
    <div style="text-align: left;">
      <img src="<%= travel_signImageBase64 %>" alt="Company Logo"
        style="max-width: 100px;max-height: 50px;margin-left: 40px;">
    </div>
  </div>


  <p>Customer Services Support Team<br>Email: <%= SupportEmail %> | Contact No: <%= SupportcontactNo %>
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 8px;"><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Interstellar Services Private Limited (“Company”) acts solely
    as a facilitator in offering and marketing a bundled product that includes travel assistance services and a travel
    insurance policy underwritten by a licensed insurance company in India. The Company is not an insurance company,
    insurance intermediary, or travel assistance service provider and does not assume any responsibility or liability
    for the underwriting, issuance, servicing, or fulfillment of the travel insurance policy or the provision of travel
    assistance services. All claims, disputes, and service-related matters are to be addressed directly with the
    respective service providers, whose terms and conditions shall govern such interactions. Customers are advised to
    carefully review the insurance policy documents/insurance certificate and service terms issued by the respective
    third parties prior to availing the services. The Company shall not be held liable for any act, omission, delay,
    denial, or deficiency in service by the third-party service providers. The Company shall extend all necessary
    assistance to its customers/members/clients.</p>

</body>

</html>